#. Plugin Name of the plugin
#: webchangedetector.php
msgid "Web Change Detector"
msgstr "Web Change Detector"

#. Plugin URI of the plugin
#. Author URI of the plugin
#: webchangedetector.php
msgid "https://www.webchangedetector.com"
msgstr "https://www.webchangedetector.com"

#. Description of the plugin
#: webchangedetector.php
msgid ""
"Detect changes on your website visually before and after updating your "
"website. You can also run automatic change detections and get notified on "
"changes of your website."
msgstr ""
"Erkenne Änderungen auf deiner Website visuell vor und nach der "
"Aktualisierung deiner Website. Du kannst auch automatische "
"Änderungserkennungen durchführen und bei Änderungen deiner Website "
"benachrichtigt werden."

#. Author of the plugin
#: webchangedetector.php
msgid "Mike Miler"
msgstr "Mike Miler"

